        <li>Runge-Kutta 4th order ODE solver built-in</li>
        <li>Statistics: mean, variance, correlation, regression</li>
        <li>Matrix: determinant, inverse, eigenvalues, SVD</li>
        <li>Complex numbers with polar/rectangular conversion</li>
        <li>Pipeline-driven data transformation for analysis</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
