  <div class="blog-grid">
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-04-17</div>
      <div class="blog-title">LATERALUS v1.9: FFI &amp; Ecosystem</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">C FFI bridge, WASM &amp; JavaScript compilation targets, Jupyter kernel, C backend visitors for all v1.6–v1.8 features. 1,549 tests, 30 examples. OS networking.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-04-16</div>
      <div class="blog-title">LATERALUS v1.8: The Metaprogramming Release</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">Procedural macros, @derive with 8 traits, const fn, reflect!(Type), quote/unquote AST transforms. 1,499 tests, 29 examples.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-04-15</div>
      <div class="blog-title">v1.7: Package Manager &amp; Build System</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">lateralus.toml manifests, semver dependency resolution, lock files, build profiles, workspaces, and @cfg conditional compilation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-04-01</div>
      <div class="blog-title">v1.6: Concurrency &amp; Async</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">async/await, nursery structured concurrency, typed channels, select multiplexing, cancellation tokens, and async for loops.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-03-31</div>
      <div class="blog-title">LateralusOS Phase 3: Interactive Desktop</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">Functional terminal with 17 commands, RAM filesystem, PC speaker audio, animated wallpaper with Fibonacci spirals, Alt+Tab, and window animations. 375KB kernel.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-03-30</div>
      <div class="blog-title">LATERALUS v1.5: The ADT Edition</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">Result::Ok, Option::Some, match-as-expression, Hindley-Milner type inference, and 1,158 passing tests. The biggest release yet.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2026-03-30</div>
      <div class="blog-title">Hacking with LATERALUS</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">Built-in SHA-256, BLAKE2b, XOR cipher, HMAC tokens, and pipeline-driven data transformation — the perfect CTF toolkit.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2024-11-20</div>
      <div class="blog-title">The Self-Hosting Journey</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">How we're writing the LATERALUS compiler in LATERALUS — the bootstrap problem, v2 stages, and what it means.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="blog-card">
      <div class="blog-date">2024-11-15</div>
      <div class="blog-title">Pipeline Operators: A Deep Dive</div>
      <div class="blog-excerpt">How |&gt; desugars in the AST, why optional pipelines matter, and the zero-overhead guarantee.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

