    <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-dot complete"></div><div class="tl-content"><div class="tl-version">v1.7 — Package Manager<span class="tl-tag done">complete</span></div><div class="tl-desc">lateralus.toml manifests, semver dependency resolution, lock files, build profiles, workspaces, @cfg conditional compilation.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-dot complete"></div><div class="tl-content"><div class="tl-version">v1.8 — Metaprogramming<span class="tl-tag done">complete</span></div><div class="tl-desc">Procedural macros, @derive system (8 traits), const fn, reflect!(Type), quote/unquote AST transforms, comptime blocks.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-dot current"></div><div class="tl-content"><div class="tl-version">v1.9 — FFI &amp; Ecosystem<span class="tl-tag now">current</span></div><div class="tl-desc">C FFI bridge, WASM &amp; JavaScript targets, Jupyter kernel, C backend v1.6–v1.8 visitors, OS networking. 1,549 tests.</div></div></div>
    <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-dot future"></div><div class="tl-content"><div class="tl-version">v2.0 — Self-Hosted</div><div class="tl-desc">LATERALUS compiler written in LATERALUS. Full bootstrap: lexer, parser, codegen in .ltl source.</div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

